                     <note type="general">54 lines</note>
                     <note type="general">Written in four columns along the fibers on the recto; written across the fibers on the verso in a different hand</note>
                     <note type="general">Upper margin of 1.5 cm.; lower margin of at least 1 cm</note>
                     <note type="general">Extracted from mummy cartonnage with P.Duk.inv. 699 and P.Duk.inv. 701-704</note>
                     <note type="general">P.Duk.inv. 700 R was formerly P.Duk.inv. MF79 27 R</note>
